            <editable rel="page" field="content_body" ><p><span style="font-size: small;">Our personnel bring decades of billing and coding experience. &nbsp;Many other firms have billers who are able to complete rudimentary data entry. &nbsp;Exemplar Health Resources invests in our billing and coding team ensuring our personnel are certified coding professionals with the skill set to code your claims with precision to maximize reimbursements and accurately code to prevent payers audits, refunds, and write-offs.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: small;">With anatomical and physiological training coupled with ICD-9, ICD-10, CPT, and HCPCS training, we ensure coding excellence for all procedures and encounters. &nbsp;Our coding team has extensive experience with CMS, Medicare, Medicaid, and commercial insurance carriers to successfully achieve reimbursements for our clients.</span></p>
<h2>ICD-10</h2>
<p><span style="font-size: small;">Our team is prepared for ICD-10 and we are assisting our practices for the ICD-10 switch coming in 2013. &nbsp;We work in tandem with your payers to identify goals and objectives to minimize the disruption to either coding processes, and determine the changes your payers are implementing with the subsequent deadlines for their claims submission policies due to the ICD-10 changes.</span></p></editable>
